5. Grammar in a love story - Notice grammar structures in a story

The summary of "Five days to fall in love"
After Salim‚Äôs relationship had ended, he decided to be a better boyfriend. 
However, he had no girlfriend to be a better boyfriend to. 
He set himself a rather impossible challenge - finding a girlfriend and 
making her fall in love with him in only five days.

start a new relationship
He wants to find a new girlfriend and be a great boyfriend to her.

After Salim‚Äôs relationship had ended, he decided to be a better boyfriend.
However, he had no girlfriend to be a better boyfriend to.
He wants to find a girlfriend and make her fall in love with him.

Part 1
I‚Äôve been single for exactly 360 days. According to my conservative mother, 
it‚Äôs too long. ‚ÄúWhen I was your age, I'd already had you, and you'd already 
